            <p class="text-[10px] text-kernel-500 mt-2">
              Parallel loop: Cortex → Putamen → GP → Thalamus → Cortex (basal ganglia circuit).
              Dopaminergic modulation from substantia nigra. Parkinson's disrupts this loop.
