          </div>
          <div class="bg-kernel-950 rounded p-4 border border-kernel-800">
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-amber-400 mb-2">Memory Circuit (Papez)</h4>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] text-kernel-400 flex-wrap">
